longDescription:
Visit my website: Pablo Wunderlich 

Sound Cloud demo: Complete Mysterious Forest Game Music Pack


Complete Mysterious Forest Game Music Pack is inspired by the music in games such as Ori, Limbo, and Kena. It is simple and rich in textures that evoque vibes of suspense, mystery, and ethereal divinity.


============================

IS THIS MUSIC RIGHT FOR MY GAME?

============================

If you need music with suspense, mystical, mysterious, and ethereal vibes then this is for you.

Learn more about Pablo at www.pablowunderlich.com

Technical details

Contains the following:

  • 41 original high-quality WAV tracks (16-bit / 44.1 kHz)


  • Music: 15 songs and LOOPS. All the songs LOOP for your convenience. There's also an unlooped version in case you would need it.


  • 1. Intro Song
  • 2. Splash Screen and Menu
  • 3. Exploration Cue 1
  • 4. Exploration Cue 2
  • 5. Exploration Cue 3
  • 6. Tension Cue 1
  • 7. Tension Cue 2
  • 8. Tension Cue 3
  • 9. Action/Battle Cue 1
  • 10. Action/Battle Cue 2
  • 11. Action/Battle Cue 3
  • 12. Mood - Sad song
  • 13. Mood - Sentimental song
  • 14. Mood - Victory song
  • 15. The End/Credist song


  • Stingers: 9


  • 1. Stinger 1
  • 2. Stinger 2
  • 3. Stinger 3
  • 4. You died variation 1
  • 5. You died variation 2
  • 6. Found something 1
  • 7. Found something 2
  • 8. Found something 3
  • 9. Found somethig 4


  • SFX: 17


  • 1. Deep Giant Moan 1
  • 2. Deep Giant Moan 2
  • 3. Deep Giant Moan 3
  • 4. Deep Giant Moan 4
  • 5. Deep Giant Moan 5
  • 6. Deep Giant Moan 6
  • 7. Deep Giant Moan with drums
  • 8. Forest 1
  • 9. Forest 2

  • 11. Forest 4
  • 12. Forest calling you 1
  • 13. Forest calling you 2
  • 14. Forest calling you 3
  • 15. Forest calling you 4
  • 16. Forest calline you 5
  • 17. Thunder


  • Unlimited Royalty-Free license
